1
00:00:14,080 --> 00:00:15,634
Which is the way out?
哪条是出去的路

2
00:00:15,714 --> 00:00:17,965
There's an area they don't allow us to go.
有一个他们禁止我们去的地方

3
00:00:18,160 --> 00:00:20,137
If I was a guessing person,
让我猜的话

4
00:00:20,605 --> 00:00:23,668
I'd guess that's the closest thing this place has to an exit.
那里一定就相当于这地方的出口

5
00:00:38,971 --> 00:00:41,897
Wait. Someone's coming.
等等  有人来了

6
00:01:04,422 --> 00:01:06,125
What's that sound?
那是什么声音

7
00:01:11,382 --> 00:01:13,314
There's something inside.
里面有东西

8
00:01:18,240 --> 00:01:21,325
These are daemons without humans.
这些都是没有人类的精灵

9
00:01:21,405 --> 00:01:22,502
David.
大卫

10
00:01:24,948 --> 00:01:26,537
Shay.
雪伊

11
00:01:31,268 --> 00:01:32,685
Bridget.
布里奇特

12
00:01:33,450 --> 00:01:35,542
These daemons belong to the children
这些精灵都属于那些

13
00:01:35,611 --> 00:01:38,514
who've been taken and not come back.
被带走就再没回来的孩子

14
00:01:51,737 --> 00:01:53,005
That's Billy.
那是比利

15
00:01:53,154 --> 00:01:55,005
His daemon is gone.
他的精灵不见了

16
00:01:56,120 --> 00:01:57,691
That means...
那意味着

17
00:01:58,708 --> 00:02:02,114
-I'm sorry, Roger. -You knew?
-我很难过  罗杰  -你早就知道了

18
00:02:03,245 --> 00:02:05,028
I found him.
我找到了他

19
00:02:05,680 --> 00:02:07,028
Before he died.
在他死之前

20
00:02:07,394 --> 00:02:10,034
He got out of here somehow.
他不知用什么办法逃出了这里

21
00:02:12,102 --> 00:02:14,228
I helped him find his ma.
我帮他找到了他妈妈

22
00:02:15,908 --> 00:02:17,714
Lyra...
莱拉

23
00:02:18,994 --> 00:02:22,662
...if the daemons are alive, where are the children?
如果精灵还活着  那孩子们去哪了

24
00:02:29,234 --> 00:02:38,960
Seven, eight, nine, ten...
七  八  九  十

25
00:02:39,508 --> 00:02:43,710
One, two, three..
一  二  三

26
00:02:43,931 --> 00:02:45,710
Was Billy like this?
比利也是这副样子吗

27
00:02:45,748 --> 00:02:46,971
Yes.
是的

28
00:02:47,040 --> 00:02:48,971
We can't end up here.
我们不能变成那样

29
00:02:50,445 --> 00:02:52,034
The alarm's stopped.
警报停了

30
00:02:54,091 --> 00:02:55,760
We have to get back.
我们得回去了

31
00:02:56,960 --> 00:02:58,582
Lyra!
莱拉

